<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/26112603">在国内谈笑风生的人，在国外用英文和人交流时还能保持那么幽默吗？会不会显得sometimes naive？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="2627926" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content"></div>


</div>
